This repository contains the GPU-enabled implementation of MGVB

To run it copy mgvb_2026_cuda, focused_cMGVB.sh, PEP_for_gMGVB.R, and 
sqlite_script.sql to your MGVB/bin directory. Edit lines 31 and 32 
of focused_cMGVB.sh to include full path to the R script and sql script.
Edit config files as for MGVB runs. Then, from within your raw files 
directory execute focused_cMGVB.sh.
